Package hep.tuple.interfaces

Interface Summary
FillableTuple An interface implemented by all mutable tuples.
FillableTupleColumn An interface implemented by all TupleColumns that can be filled.
FTuple An interface implemented by all Tuples.
FTupleColumn An interface implemented by all TupleColumns
FTupleCursor A TupleCursor is used to step through the rows of an Tuple
FTupleEvent  
FTupleFactory A TupleFactory is used to create new FillableTuples and FillableTupleColumns.
FTupleListener  
HasFTuple
